# MCPB bundle build artifact (produced by `npx @anthropic-ai/mcpb pack`; attached to
# GitHub Releases, never committed). The manifest.json + .mcpbignore source files ARE tracked.
*.mcpb

# Claude Code plugin: the assembled tree at /plugin/ IS committed on purpose — it is the
# marketplace `source` (.claude-plugin/marketplace.json), so `/plugin marketplace add` clones a
# repo that already contains the built plugin. Do NOT ignore it. Its runtime cruft (.venv/,
# __pycache__/, *.egg-info/) is already covered by the rules above. Rebuild with
# `uv run python -m scripts.build_plugin` and commit the result. (`dist/` stays for scratch builds.)

